{"tid":399010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張仁良馬時亨品格日齊放飛機","createTime":"2017-09-13T15:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T15:47:21.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f84034521ea6ab3d9e1a1319c0b5dae83e4cb4b","tid":399010,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"《言歸政傳》大學民主牆風波講左幾日都未平息，「責無旁貸」嘅教育大學校長張仁良究竟調查到肇事者嘅身份未呢？Ｊｅｎｎｙ同一眾行家都好關注事態發展，等咗咁多日喇！今日見到採訪通知上邊有佢個名，仲拍埋校董會主席馬時亨一齊出席今年嘅「香港品格日」活動，咁應景<br />\n？Ｊｅｎｎｙ點都要過嚟望望先！<br />\n　<br />\n＊張仁良馬時亨齊「放飛機」＊<br />\n　<br />\n　　唔知係唔係佢哋兩位呢排太Ｈｉｔ啦，Ｊｅｎｎｙ一去到見到好多行家，明顯就係等緊佢哋兩個嘅出現。只不過望返份新聞稿，咦？點解冇佢哋兩個個名嘅？拿拿臨去搵個ＰＲ問問先！<br />\n　　原來佢哋兩位今朝早齊齊「放飛機」，唔通係因為佢哋都Ｆｅｅｌ到呢個活動「太特別」？<br />\n明嘅！兩位都係唔想答返之前答過嘅嘢令到大家冇癮啫！好彩仲有個好耐都冇出嚟講吓嘢嘅行會召集人陳智思（Ｂｅｒｎａｒｄ）出現啫，Ｊｅｎｎｙ先不至於白行一轉咋！<br />\n　　都係Ｂｅｒｎａｒｄ最心水清，完咗個活動就主動行埋嚟話：「你哋都係等張仁良呀呢？」<br />\n哎呀！Ｂｅｒｎａｒｄ，你都好重要㗎！就算張校長有嚟，你要講嘢嘅話我哋梗係會聽啦！"},{"pid":"8a5066a0d259527871c5293c209846486770eb0d","tid":399010,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd59f88a01dd2a328fee80fd5b51cf0e1003085","tid":399010,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"香港就係太多呢D濕鳩做官"},{"pid":"fe6273bbf9db7d8258ecb83be9fc935cef29a6bb","tid":399010,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c517a461497c499e869c69462a49c66c8a949a","tid":399010,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676774f8e3249dd51912f8dc4ef21a19a7b35197","tid":399010,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"屌你龜縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4632d17fc15dbe35c496137ce4e3eba304a8390","tid":399010,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:47:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你龜縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n&quot;張仁良龜兒子&quot; <br />\n&quot;馬時亨龜兒子&quot;"}]}